<div class="bg-white py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-32">
    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#00334E] mb-6">
          Screening solutions that meet your needs
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          We partner with you to design a screening program that fits your hiring objectives, or help you choose from our pre-bundled packages. Our FCRA-certified, Puerto Rico based team is standing by to answer any screening, compliance, or how-to questions that either you or your candidates have, and we keep you both updated about the status of your employment background check
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-100 aspect-video rounded-2xl"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2 -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1 bg-gray-100 aspect-video rounded-2xl"></div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#00334E] mb-6">
          Complete automated process: 100% paper-free.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Our state-of-the-art software allows for a fully automated process, which ensure a direct and secure communication channel with both the candidates and your office. We take care of everything: From contacting the candidates, gathering information, obtaining digital signatures and send reports to your unique custom account, which we create for you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3 -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#00334E] mb-6">
          A well trained, bilingual team of researchers with offices in Puerto Rico.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#00AEEF] mb-4">
          Our team has more than ten years of background check experience in both US and Puerto Rico markets.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          We know how to manage local requests and screenings, which many times requires in person requests at government offices or institutions. Only a company with staff on the field can do that. That is the SmartScreening Advantage
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-100 aspect-video rounded-2xl"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
